race.description: Sungold Milk Saputo Dairy Australia Maiden Plate
race.comment: TITANIC (2) was beaten less than 2L at Stawell on debut. Kept ticking over with a recent trial win at Geelong. Worth plenty of thought with the extra fitness and learning. ROCK GLORY (8) peaks and is better placed back to country level. Had excuses at Cranbourne last time and the form she displayed in her initial preparation reads extra well. She can use the inside gate to advantage and a much-improved effort is on the cards. THE TORONADO KID (9) also presents fourth up and will also find this easier than the provincials. Maps well and has switched yards on a 37-day return. IMMORTAL JUSTICE (5) has an outside barrier but should be around the mark.
